{"tid":2313702,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「印仔開箱」氣炸吞拿魚拉絲芝士酥","createTime":"2020-12-06T04:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T10:41:50.000Z","uid":33359,"like":14,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"4f078190813c4278fdecbfb3709911caba60ebe0","tid":2313702,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zT30GxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzT30GxR.jpg&h=cf16a6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0MtQre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0MtQre.jpg&h=b5552565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VP6EW6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVP6EW6g.jpg&h=033ba800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我炸之前無上蛋漿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以出到黎D色無咁好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋炸耐咗少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吞拿魚味都幾濃郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n芝士真係拉到絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾好味吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n28蚊一包,入面有3舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圍埋7蚊舊都幾抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b863c7657d9dc08e2a8eba72ca3135111badf7a2","tid":2313702,"uid":281772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f72bcf2835a2d9ca6b6e533716bfd5a45044b5","tid":2313702,"uid":385480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2df7308581f4a01feb88cc70091b5c738cde